---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Case studies"
description: "How organisations across Africa use Engage — from an 80-role org redesign delivered in a week to a management team graded proactively ahead of growth."
permalink: /case-studies/
---
<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-inner">
    <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a><span>/</span>Case studies</div>
    <div class="eyebrow">Proof in practice</div>
    <h1>Engage in the <em>real world.</em></h1>
    <p class="lead">From an 80-role organisational redesign delivered in a single week to a nine-role management team graded with intent — see how organisations across Africa put Engage to work.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="filter-bar" data-cs-filter>
  <button class="filter-btn active" data-filter="all">All</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="east-africa">East Africa</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="southern-africa">Southern Africa</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="west-africa">West Africa</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="financial">Financial Services</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="public">Public Sector</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="ngo">NGO &amp; Development</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="private">Private Sector</button>
</div>

<section class="cases-section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="cases-grid">
      {%- for cs in collections.caseStudy %}
      <a class="case-card" data-cs-card data-tags="{{ cs.data.regionTag }} {{ cs.data.sectorTag }}" href="{{ cs.url }}">
        <div class="case-card-top">
          <div class="case-region">{{ cs.data.region }}{% if cs.data.sector %} &middot; {{ cs.data.sector }}{% endif %}</div>
          <div class="case-client">{{ cs.data.title }}</div>
          {% if cs.data.meta %}<div class="case-meta">{{ cs.data.meta }}</div>{% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="case-card-body">
          <span class="case-tag">{{ cs.data.sector }}</span>
          <p class="case-summary">{{ cs.data.abstract }}</p>
        </div>
        <span class="case-cta">Read case study <span>&rarr;</span></span>
      </a>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
